Ma'am,

944
00:58:38,300 --> 00:58:40,433
you talk too much.

945
00:58:42,533 --> 00:58:45,209
My daughter married Chairman Ga Sung Ho.

946
00:58:45,233 --> 00:58:49,300
So do you think she'll have a lot of money
or a lot of vice presidents?

947
