1002
01:01:36,667 --> 01:01:38,543
Unimaginable wealth.

1003
01:01:38,567 --> 01:01:42,809
Of course I need to survive to inherit it,
but I want to help this much.

1004
01:01:42,833 --> 01:01:44,543
How?

1005
01:01:44,567 --> 01:01:47,276
First, let's split

1006
01:01:47,300 --> 01:01:49,233
that pair of closely-knit siblings.

1007
01:02:01,367 --> 01:02:03,000
Here it comes, here it comes.

1008
01:02:07,633 --> 01:02:09,409
- Wow.
- What's this?

1009
01:02:09,433 --> 01:02:10,909
I'll eat well.

1010
01:02:10,933 --> 01:02:12,143
Miss, try some.

1011
01:02:12,167 --> 01:02:13,800
Yes.

1012
01:02:16,333 --> 01:02:17,609
Even without adding dried pollack,

1013
