on the back of the package, it tastes best.

1014
01:02:20,167 --> 01:02:23,043
Countless researchers
spent years developing this.

1015
01:02:23,067 --> 01:02:25,676
Jeez, taste it before you talk.

1016
01:02:25,700 --> 01:02:29,109
You look exactly like
the owner of a red noodle company.

1017
01:02:29,133 --> 01:02:32,567
My friend holds tons of shares
in that red noodle company.

1018
01:02:33,233 --> 01:02:38,409
But the vice president keeps causing
scandals, so the stock's crashing hard.

1019
01:02:38,433 --> 01:02:39,543
Right, friend?

1020
01:02:39,567 --> 01:02:41,567
Yeah, eat up.

1021
01:02:43,333 --> 01:02:44,909
We'll do the dishes today.

1022
01:02:44,933 --> 01:02:47,700
Oh, you don't have to.

1023
01:02:49,100 --> 01:02:50,843
I'll enjoy it.

1024
01:02:50,867 --> 01:02:52,933
Enjoy your meal.

1025
01:03:01,200 --> 01:03:02,900
Oh, my.

1026
01:03:04,833 --> 01:03:06,933
This is ridiculously good.

1027
01:03:07,767 --> 01:03:09,443
Mr. Dong Min.

1028
01:03:09,467 --> 01:03:12,309
When will you teach me this recipe?

1029
01:03:12,333 --> 01:03:13,443
I'll tell you later.

1030
01:03:13,467 --> 01:03:14,476
I'll get some water.

1031
01:03:14,500 --> 01:03:16,076
Alright.

1032
01:03:16,100 --> 01:03:17,409
We're out of makgeolli too.

1033
01:03:17,433 --> 01:03:19,367
Need to bring more.

1034
01:03:22,200 --> 01:03:23,209
Dong Min.

1035
01:03:23,233 --> 01:03:25,576
Ms. Bu Se Mi's
a 3rd-degree black belt in taekwondo.

1036
01:03:25,600 --> 01:03:27,609
Isn't that impressive?

1037
01:03:27,633 --> 01:03:31,400
She's full of surprises, I'm telling you.

1038
01:03:33,200 --> 01:03:34,576
She really has a knack for
surprising people in all sorts of ways.

1039
01:03:34,600 --> 01:03:36,600
- Sorry, the ointment...
- You okay?

1040
01:03:37,233 --> 01:03:39,433
Ugh, seriously.

1041
01:03:44,867 --> 01:03:46,567
Ms. Kim Yeong Ran.

1042
01:03:51,867 --> 01:03:52,876
What? What?

1043
01:03:52,900 --> 01:03:53,943
Broth got in my eye.

1044
01:03:53,967 --> 01:03:55,933
- Dried pollack, yes.
- Dried pollack!

1045
01:04:00,100 --> 01:04:02,476
[Muchang Supermarket,
881st Lottery 1st Prize Winner]

1046
01:04:02,500 --> 01:04:04,300
