kindergarten class.

1049
01:04:18,167 --> 01:04:20,376
No way.

1050
01:04:20,400 --> 01:04:23,443
No, drink a bit more.

1051
01:04:23,467 --> 01:04:28,443
I'm being utterly adorable right now.

1052
01:04:28,467 --> 01:04:31,167
- Miss, can you have just one more drink?
- No, thanks.

1053
01:04:32,833 --> 01:04:33,909
My friend.

1054
01:04:33,933 --> 01:04:35,767
Don't mess this up.

1055
01:04:36,667 --> 01:04:39,533
Are you worried about me?

1056
01:04:40,433 --> 01:04:42,533
Don't sweat it, pal.

1057
01:04:47,667 --> 01:04:48,909
I'll take my leave first.

1058
01:04:48,933 --> 01:04:50,943
- Go ahead.
- Let's go together.

1059
01:04:50,967 --> 01:04:53,009
I've got an early start tomorrow too.

1060
01:04:53,033 --> 01:04:55,243
Then I should head out early too.

1061
01:04:55,267 --> 01:04:57,043
No, you stay and drink more.

1062
01:04:57,067 --> 01:04:58,343
Let's go together.

1063
01:04:58,367 --> 01:04:59,743
Bye, Dong Min.

1064
01:04:59,767 --> 01:05:01,276
What's the occasion, Jeon Dong Min?

1065
01:05:01,300 --> 01:05:03,067
Escort her properly.

1066
01:05:10,400 --> 01:05:12,133
Let's go together, Miss.

1067
01:05:13,433 --> 01:05:16,209
They look really good together.

1068
01:05:16,233 --> 01:05:18,176
- Huh?
- Tae Min.

1069
01:05:18,200 --> 01:05:20,009
- Did the spirit say that?
- No, I did.

1070
01:05:20,033 --> 01:05:22,176
Come on.

1071
01:05:22,200 --> 01:05:24,043
Let me pour you a drink.

1072
01:05:24,067 --> 01:05:25,967
Ms. Hye Ji, you're cute.

1073
01:05:28,867 --> 01:05:30,567
You're dead.

1074
01:05:32,000 --> 01:05:36,433
You're killing me.

1075
01:05:57,500 --> 01:05:59,967
Do you have something to say to me?

1076
01:06:01,867 --> 01:06:05,267
You've been staring me like
you have something to say since earlier.

1077
01:06:06,267 --> 01:06:08,800
Now here, back at the supermarket too.

1078
01:06:12,867 --> 01:06:14,843
Forget it, say it another time.

1079
01:06:14,867 --> 01:06:17,133
I'm too exhausted today.

1080
01:06:19,067 --> 01:06:20,733
Ms. Kim Yeong Ran.

1081
01:06:26,900 --> 01:06:31,809
♫ Starting to be born again ♫

1082
01:06:31,833 --> 01:06:33,667
You are Kim Yeong Ran, right?

1083
01:06:45,000 --> 01:06:48,109
♫ Now is the time ♫

1084
01:06:48,133 --> 01:06:56,076
♫ Even hidden scars will shine ♫

1085
01:06:56,100 --> 01:06:59,209
♫ I share the light ♫

1086
01:06:59,233 --> 01:07:05,976
♫ I'll brighten the days
shrouded in darkness ♫

1087
01:07:06,000 --> 01:07:08,009
♫ It's not over ♫

1088
01:07:08,033 --> 01:07:16,033
♫ The present isn't bound by the past ♫

1089
01:07:16,467 --> 01:07:22,309
♫ Come back to me safely ♫

1090
01:07:22,333 --> 01:07:28,133
♫ So I'm, I'm alive ♫

1091
01:07:29,733 --> 01:07:33,809
♫ From the untouchable darkness ♫

1092
01:07:33,833 --> 01:07:39,376
♫ Starting to be born again ♫

1093
01:07:39,400 --> 01:07:44,676
♫ For the new me about to begin ♫

1094
01:07:44,700 --> 01:07:50,509
♫ I want to sail away ♫

1095
01:07:50,533 --> 01:07:52,009
♫ Again ♫

1096
01:07:52,033 --> 01:07:53,809
♫ Show you better ♫

1097
01:07:53,833 --> 01:07:54,943
♫ Enclose the letters of the past ♫

1098
01:07:54,967 --> 01:07:56,709
Jeon Dong Min knows my true identity.

1099
01:07:56,733 --> 01:07:58,076
Are you afraid I'll say something?

1100
01:07:58,100 --> 01:08:00,009
She's just someone
who only stayed at school.

1101
01:08:00,033 --> 01:08:01,609
What does he know about management?

1102
01:08:01,633 --> 01:08:03,309
You want me to expose this?

1103
01:08:03,333 --> 01:08:05,209
We didn't recognize a tiger cub, did we?

1104
01:08:05,233 --> 01:08:07,009
You're terrified of your sister, aren't you?

1105
01:08:07,033 --> 01:08:08,909
What exactly do you two want?

1106
01:08:08,933 --> 01:08:10,843
I love this place.

1107
01:08:10,867 --> 01:08:12,776
I'll make sure you two rot in jail.

1108
01:08:12,800 --> 01:08:14,809
Ms. Bu Se Mi got arrested.

1109
01:08:14,833 --> 01:08:15,876
No, background check.

1110
01:08:15,900 --> 01:08:16,909
Oh, Lord.

1111
01:08:16,933 --> 01:08:19,743
Let's go. Search every possible spot.

1112
01:08:19,767 --> 01:08:21,376
Hey, get down!

1113
01:08:21,400 --> 01:08:23,533
I'll leave Muchang.
